1
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:06,960
To think an assassin snuck into the Marquis's Manor.

2
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:08,120
How novel.

3
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:16,320
Who are you?

4
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:17,960
Where is the Princess?

5
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:19,560
Father, who is this?

6
00:01:20,039 --> 00:01:20,900
Do you know her?

7
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,020
I remember you.

8
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:25,520
You used to be the Grassland King's handmaid.

9
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:26,840
I am Wu Yue.

10
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:29,240
I used to serve the Princess Consort.

11
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:31,640
Princess Consort? What Princess Consort?

12
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,979
What are you doing in Dasheng?

13
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:36,050
Because the Princess is in danger.

14
00:01:36,479 --> 00:01:38,520
Brother, what are they talking about?

15
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:40,580
Why can't I understand a word? Do you?

16
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:41,560
No.

17
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:44,100
Huanghuacai, do you understand?

18
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,120
Ten years ago,

19
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:48,920
there was a Han woman by the Grassland King's side.

20
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:51,420
The Princess Consort you speak of is her.

21
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,080
You know quite a lot.

22
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,820
I am from the Song Army.

23
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,800
I see.

24
00:01:57,039 --> 00:02:00,800
What do you mean the Princess is in danger?

25
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:03,170
There is a new omen from the Grassland.

26
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:06,320
It says the Princess is being haunted by something evil.

27
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:07,450
I have come this time

28
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:09,380
to take her back to the Grassland.

29
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,420
Can you stop speaking in riddles?

30
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,300
The Princess she speaks of

31
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,280
is Chuyi.

32
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,450
What did you say?

33
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:18,800
Chuyi?

34
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:21,040
How can Chuyi be a princess?

35
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:23,640
Chuyi's mother was a Han woman.

36
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:27,320
She served as a medic for the Bai Army back then

37
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,780
and went to the border with me.

38
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:31,280
Later,

39
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,640
at the border,

40
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,440
she saved the critically ill Grassland King.

41
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:38,640
Without knowing his identity,

42
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:42,360
she fell in love with the Grassland King over time,

43
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,560
and had Chuyi.

44
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:55,640
If this had been discovered back then,

45
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:56,880
it would have been a capital crime.

46
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:59,520
Later, after the Grassland King recovered,

47
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:01,240
he took Chuyi's mother away.

48
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,200
However,

49
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:06,000
since the Yueshi Kingdom and Dasheng were enemies,

50
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:08,040
it was a hurdle the Princess Consort could not overcome.

51
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:10,160
So she became heartsick,

52
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,900
and passed away from illness soon after.

53
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:15,320
Before Chuyi's mother passed away,

54
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,260
she entrusted Chuyi to me.

55
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,560
Hoping I could hide her identity

56
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:22,060
and let her grow up as an ordinary person.

57
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:25,360
So she is the child the Princess Consort gave her life for,

58
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:28,520
yet you've kept her locked up in this place for over ten years.

59
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,560
I must take her away today.

60
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,120
You cannot take her.

61
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:32,720
What?

62
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,400
Do you intend to keep her by force?

63
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,660
Her surname is Bai now.

64
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,690
She is under my care.

65
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,640
And I swear to Heaven,

66
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,930
right now, other than my Bai Manor,

67
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:45,000
there is no place safer than here.

68
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:48,360
Wait. Chuyi is in danger.

69
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,720
That means besides us...

70
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,280
Someone else knows Chuyi's identity,

71
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,520
and has targeted her.

72
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,720
You're right.

73
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:56,960
That is true.

74
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:59,960
Is the person targeting her from our Dasheng Kingdom,

75
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,240
or from the Yueshi Kingdom?

76
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:04,040
I'm guessing it's someone from the Yueshi Kingdom.

77
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:07,760
And this person doesn't seem to want Chuyi's identity exposed.

78
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:10,890
Otherwise, we would have heard something by now.

79
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:15,480
So the best solution is to hand the Princess over to me.

80
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,760
I'll take her back to the grasslands.

81
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:17,160
No.

82
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:18,320
Why not?

83
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,680
The enemy is in the shadows right now.

84
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,960
If Chuyi goes back to the grasslands with you now,

85
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:25,220
the journey will be fraught with danger.

86
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:28,000
Then do you have a better plan?

87
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:31,380
Until the person targeting Chuyi reveals themselves,

88
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:33,320
we have to stay put.

89
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:37,040
And it's best if you don't see her right now.

90
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:39,600
Why? She is my Princess.

91
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,600
It's only right that I stay by her side.

92
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:44,560
Chuyi is shy with strangers.

93
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,490
I'm afraid you might scare her.

94
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,360
Ridiculous.

95
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:14,720
Manchuan, you finally came to see me.

96
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,620
I'm here to ask you something.

97
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,160
Go ahead.

98
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,760
Regarding the Song family's military funds case back then,

99
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,880
the accounts were short by five hundred thousand taels of silver.

100
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:26,810
Did you have anything to do with it?

101
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,240
You suspect me?

102
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,490
Answer my question.

103
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,120
Why would I touch the military funds?

104
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:34,960
I've looked at the Bai family ledgers countless times.

105
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,960
Although the accountant from back then went missing,

106
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,680
what's fake is fake.

107
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,280
There are always flaws.

108
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:42,080
So, you really are suspecting me.

109
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:43,540
I'm asking you a question.

110
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,540
You don't trust me.

111
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,000
She is my wife.

112
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,380
I have to investigate.

113
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,810
Even if it means investigating me?

114
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:00,940
I was the one who met you first.

115
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,380
I was the one who met you first.

116
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,680
Do you want to hear the truth?

117
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:11,680
Go ahead.

118
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,080
The truth is,

119
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,120
I like you.

120
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:21,160
From the moment I first saw you,

121
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,480
I knew I was done for.

122
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,680
I can calculate people's hearts,

123
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,140
and assess the situation.

124
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,320
I know who to get close to,

125
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,360
and who to stay away from.

126
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,420
But you are the only one

127
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,480
I dare not touch,

128
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,570
yet can't bear to let go.

129
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,460
You shouldn't have fallen for me.

130
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,360
But I fell for you anyway.

131
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:49,890
If I told you I was the one who destroyed the Song Army,

132
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,159
what would you do?

133
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,040
You're so smart.

134
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:55,180
You shouldn't have gone this far.

135
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:56,520
What about you?

136
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,560
Have you ever, for a single moment,

137
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:01,480
even just one moment, thought about loving me back?

138
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,480
No.

139
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,610
I don't believe you.

140
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:14,440
Manchuan, I know you're suspecting me,

141
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,480
not for Song Xuan,

142
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,560
and not for the evidence.

143
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:21,320
It's to completely cut me out of your heart,

144
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:24,180
so that not even a shadow remains.

145
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,680
Are you crazy?

146
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,720
I'm helping you make a clean break.

147
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,520
Nonsense.

148
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,280
You came to save me after all.

149
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:36,010
Manchuan, you do have feelings for me, don't you?

150
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,920
Stop talking.

151
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,640
I also looked into the Song family's accounts.

152
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:44,280
It's a pity you asked too late.

153
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:45,690
What do you mean?

154
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:51,600
My father has already destroyed all the evidence.

155
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:03,120
Husband, do you have something to say to me?

156
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:05,800
Miss.

157
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:08,280
Miss, the Third Prince is here.

158
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,410
Why is the Third Prince here again?

159
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:13,520
Song Xuan, I need your help with something.

160
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:17,280
Third Prince, there are plenty of capable people in the capital.

161
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:19,360
Why do you keep targeting my wife?

162
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:22,120
Something happened at the academy Chuyi attends.

163
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:24,120
What? Something happened to Chuyi?

164
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:25,600
No, not Chuyi.

165
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,840
It's the academy.

166
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:27,760
What happened?

167
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:28,560
The Ministry of Justice reported that

168
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:30,280
several children disappeared for no reason.

169
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:32,679
Their bodies were found in the woods miles away.

170
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:35,919
When found, it looked like they had been mauled by a monster.

171
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,960
Then I'll go to the academy to pick up Chuyi.

172
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,120
Brother Bai, don't rush.

173
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:41,159
Lord Bai and Zhaohua have already gone.

174
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,039
As far as I know,

175
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:45,120
there has never been a beast attack in the capital.

176
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,250
At Chuyi's academy,

177
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,120
children are only allowed to go home

178
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,880
on the first and fifteenth of the month.

179
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:51,540
Outsiders can't get in at all.

180
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,760
It should be very safe.

181
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,420
So how did they go missing?

182
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:57,560
And how did they get so far away?

183
00:08:57,760 --> 00:08:58,920
What has the Ministry of Justice found?

184
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:00,920
They claim it was a monster attack.

185
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:03,320
But the wounds are unidentifiable.

186
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:06,520
Rumors are already spreading that it's the work of a demon.

187
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,650
There are no demons.

188
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,560
Clearly, they can't solve the case,

189
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,960
so they're blaming it on the supernatural.

190
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,200
Song Xuan.

191
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:15,280
I know how good you are at solving cases.

192
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:16,480
For the sake of the children,

193
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,320
I want to ask you to handle this personally.

194
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,160
Okay, I'll investigate with you.

195
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:21,020
I'm coming too.

196
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:23,320
This isn't a game.

197
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,300
I'll wait for you outside.

198
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:32,640
Huanghuacai, what do you mean?

199
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,560
Do you think I'll hold you back?

200
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:35,080
No.

201
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,250
Then let me tell you something too.

202
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:40,160
About the military payroll embezzlement case back then,

203
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,560
Shen Lingbo is innocent.

204
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,280
What did you say?

205
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:45,280
It was Shen Zhao who set it up.

206
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,420
Did you go see Shen Lingbo?

207
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:48,850
Never mind that.

208
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,480
You just trust her like that?

209
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:50,960
Yes.

210
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,720
Bai Manchuan.

211
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:56,120
I won't allow you to let your emotions cloud your judgment on this.

212
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,080
Huanghuacai.

213
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,960
I'm telling you a clue about the case,

214
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,640
and you're questioning me about this?

215
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:04,770
Can you tell the difference between a clue and feelings?

216
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:44,680
It's late, why aren't you asleep?

217
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:45,840
Miss.

218
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:49,040
Are you upset about Master Bai

219
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:49,920
and Miss Shen?

220
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:52,200
I've had it too easy lately.

221
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:55,840
I forgot why I married into the Marquis of Zhongyi's manor.

222
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:58,960
Master Bai and Miss Shen have known each other for so long.

223
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:02,320
It's understandable that he believes her.

224
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:06,170
Bai Manchuan can trust whomever he wants.

225
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,480
But what matters is

226
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:10,280
we solve our own problems.

227
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:12,320
Someone might know

228
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:15,880
the whereabouts of the missing Song Family Army squad.

229
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:17,120
Is the information reliable?

230
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:19,080
It's that woman named Ji Ruyu.

231
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:22,720
They say her gambling house secretly collects information.

232
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:26,840
She might know the whereabouts of the last squad from back then.

233
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,020
Then let's go find her.

234
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,240
Yes, Miss.
